classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
Introduction
============

Override the state menu to show all states in the workflow chain.

Version 1.8 is compatible with Plone >= 4.3.

Version 1.7 is compatible with Plone < 4.3.

Changelog
=========

1.9 - Unreleased
----------------


1.8 - 2013-10-24
----------------

* Plone 4.3 compatibility

1.7 - 2013-02-13
----------------

* Added override of contenthistory view and content_history template
  to display items from all workflows in an object's chain

1.0 - Unreleased
----------------

* Initial release
